{"tid":1026931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優紗倉真菜披嫁衣宣佈結婚","createTime":"2019-02-18T12:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T12:44:03.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5922effa4dbc3c83a8e62040e6e67ec710db9bda","tid":1026931,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"紗倉真菜稱得上是AV界紅人，身為SOD集團一姐的她，近日驚傳婚訊，紗倉竟公開在教堂內披上嫁衣的照片宣佈結婚，這個消息一度嚇壞廣大麻甩Fans。<br />\n<br />\n紗倉真菜曾在著作小說中表示入行當AV女優後已對戀愛沒有任何期待，更不期待有人愛上自己，形容自己已放棄愛人或被愛的感受。其實，紗倉真菜今次只是為Abema_Prime網上節目安排替自己舉行婚禮，當日她到位於表參道的婚禮場地Charmant Sina Tokyo，並有神父作見證，紗倉真菜自言結婚一事沒有花假，不過只是沒有新郎哥，換句話講，紗倉真菜是自己嫁給自己而已，她披上婚紗亦只是個噱頭，粉絲們又無必要太過傷心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190218/large/1550485585_f449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190218%2Flarge%2F1550485585_f449.jpg&h=343d1453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49bc8045850537d20ef59e0cd69a23b68e492b97","tid":1026931,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4cb9869996f846d20b4a61f6cb54882cbb16756","tid":1026931,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"紗倉真菜自言結婚一事沒有花假，不過只是沒有新郎哥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n?????俾人屌到弱智？"},{"pid":"60f3aed02c4e7823180feb76fc19d4b8134f9848","tid":1026931,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:41:51.000Z","msg":"睇黎下一套應該係著住婚紗屌<br />\n話唔定限定首發係送婚紗頭飾唔係底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824c4d4c14be54bb22b804b704375248ecfe2443","tid":1026931,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8fe52632f2348740e35980bbb4e955a16eca2a","tid":1026931,"uid":402,"like":1,"dislike